91
00:05:30,294 --> 00:05:31,627
I am surprised.

92
00:05:31,661 --> 00:05:35,194
I really had no idea you've
been able to see us, Orihime.

93
00:05:35,227 --> 00:05:37,361
For how long?

94
00:05:37,394 --> 00:05:40,127
-Ever since the incident
with my brother.

95
00:05:40,161 --> 00:05:44,794
-Oh, makes sense.

96
00:05:44,827 --> 00:05:46,661
-I don't think I've ever
properly thanked you

97
00:05:46,694 --> 00:05:48,594
for everything you did for him.

98
00:05:48,627 --> 00:05:51,061
By guiding his spirit
on the other side,

99
00:05:51,094 --> 00:05:52,961
he's finally in a place
where all he knows

100
00:05:52,994 --> 00:05:55,027
is peace and happiness now.

101
00:05:55,061 --> 00:05:56,227
