Ichigo to have fun.

128
00:07:35,894 --> 00:07:37,261
Why don't you play
a game of truth

129
00:07:37,294 --> 00:07:41,127
or dare with your dear old dad.

130
00:07:41,161 --> 00:07:42,327
-You're so weird.

131
00:07:42,361 --> 00:07:44,294
Couldn't you act a little
bit more like a grownup?

132
00:07:44,327 --> 00:07:46,827
-Oh, it hurts me to
see you two fighting.

133
00:07:46,861 --> 00:07:49,361
-Oh, not half as much
as it's hurting me.

134
00:07:49,394 --> 00:07:50,261
