tone of your voice.

155
00:08:55,094 --> 00:08:56,394
-Hit a nerve, did I?

156
00:08:56,427 --> 00:08:59,061
Well, don't worry,
Mr. Officer, now you

157
00:08:59,094 --> 00:09:01,694
