an insult like that.

162
00:09:06,727 --> 00:09:08,261
RUKIA (OFFSCREEN):
Tell me something.

163
00:09:10,927 --> 00:09:13,327
Am I really going to die, Renji?

164
00:09:13,361 --> 00:09:14,727
-Oh, absolutely.

165
00:09:14,761 --> 00:09:19,227
