you'll be executed immediately.

166
00:09:19,261 --> 00:09:21,427
-Very well.

167
00:09:21,461 --> 00:09:23,361
I understand.

168
00:09:23,394 --> 00:09:24,327
-Huh?

169
00:09:24,361 --> 00:09:25,694
