172
00:09:28,161 --> 00:09:29,861
-So which one is it, you idiot?

173
00:09:29,894 --> 00:09:31,327
-An idiot, huh?

174
00:09:31,361 --> 00:09:32,861
If I'm an idiot,
then how come you're

175
00:09:32,894 --> 00:09:34,194
the one locked up in the cell?

176
00:09:34,227 --> 00:09:36,661
