never stand by and do nothing

181
00:09:47,494 --> 00:09:51,394
while his own sister
faces a death sentence.

182
00:09:51,427 --> 00:09:53,494
-You're quite
correct about that.

183
00:09:53,527 --> 00:09:55,127
