184
00:09:55,161 --> 00:09:56,961
-Huh?

185
00:09:56,994 --> 00:10:01,161
-I know it for certain because
I know full well the kind of man

186
00:10:01,194 --> 00:10:02,594
he is.

187
00:10:02,627 --> 00:10:07,027
40 years have passed since I was
taken in by the Kuchiki family,

188
00:10:07,061 --> 00:10:11,461
and in all those years, he
has never once looked at me.

189
00:10:21,508 --> 00:10:22,775
[dog barking]

190
00:10:31,742 --> 00:10:35,042
-No way, this place is amazing.

191
00:10:35,075 --> 00:10:37,308
Who would have guessed
that all this time, there

192
00:10:37,342 --> 00:10:41,108
was a huge subterranean
training ground under my store?

193
00:10:41,142 --> 00:10:42,308
-Oh, forget the acting.

194
00:10:42,342 --> 00:10:44,242
Obviously, you knew this
place was down here,

195
00:10:44,275 --> 00:10:47,108
but I will admit
it's impressive.

196
00:10:47,142 --> 00:10:49,242
-So then, you wanna
get down to business?

197
00:10:49,275 --> 00:10:51,308
-Yeah, let's just
get on with it,

198
00:10:51,342 --> 00:10:53,642
this training session
or whatever you call it.

199
00:10:53,675 --> 00:10:55,542
-Always be careful
what you ask for.

200
00:10:59,508 --> 00:10:59,975
-[grunts].

201
00:11:02,842 --> 00:11:06,175
What's the big idea of knocking
me down like that, you--

202
00:11:06,208 --> 00:11:08,108
[whooshing sound]

203
00:11:08,142 --> 00:11:10,508
-It's hard to breathe when
you're in the form of a soul,

204
00:11:10,542 --> 00:11:11,908
isn't it, Ichigo?

205
00:11:11,942 --> 00:11:13,608
Right now, your
Soul Sleep, which

206
00:11:13,642 --> 00:11:15,708
is the wellspring of
your spirit energy,

207
00:11:15,742 --> 00:11:19,542
and your Soul Chain, the
booster, have been destroyed.

208
00:11:19,575 --> 00:11:22,608
So now, your soul is
like any ordinary human

209
00:11:22,642 --> 00:11:24,275
with no spiritual power.

210
00:11:24,308 --> 00:11:26,942
And so before we can
proceed, we must first

211
00:11:26,975 --> 00:11:29,808
restore the spiritual
power you have lost.

212
00:11:29,842 --> 00:11:31,975
-All right already,
just tell me what to do.

213
00:11:32,008 --> 00:11:33,108
-You're so impatient.

214
00:11:33,142 --> 00:11:34,808
All right, let's bring
out your opponent,

215
00:11:34,842 --> 00:11:36,442
and then we can start.

216
00:11:36,475 --> 00:11:38,708
Warrior, are you
ready for battle?

217
00:11:45,375 --> 00:11:47,775
-Nice to see you again, Ichigo.

218
00:11:47,808 --> 00:11:48,608
-Huh?

219
00:11:48,642 --> 00:11:50,042
-Here's your first lesson.

220
00:11:50,075 --> 00:11:52,408
You must go up against
Ururu one on one.

221
00:11:52,442 --> 00:11:53,208
-Huh?

222
00:11:53,242 --> 00:11:54,808
-The rules are quite simple.

223
00:11:54,842 --> 00:11:56,708
Lesson one is over
when one of you

224
00:11:56,742 --> 00:11:58,975
is no longer able to
continue the match.

225
00:11:59,008 --> 00:12:01,842
If you can, I suggest going
for the knockout punch.

226
00:12:01,875 --> 00:12:02,908
-Are you kidding?

227
00:12:02,942 --> 00:12:04,808
You expect me to
punch a little girl?

228
00:12:04,842 --> 00:12:06,542
-It's always dangerous
to underestimate

229
00:12:06,575 --> 00:12:07,475
your opponent, Ichigo.

230
00:12:09,542 --> 00:12:11,908
URURU (OFFSCREEN): Please put
on all this protective gear,

231
00:12:11,942 --> 00:12:12,675
Ichigo.

232
00:12:12,708 --> 00:12:15,408
