233
00:12:15,442 --> 00:12:16,708
-This whole thing's ridiculous.

234
00:12:16,742 --> 00:12:18,308
I'm not fighting her.

235
00:12:24,508 --> 00:12:26,908
-We tried to warn
him, didn't we?

236
00:12:31,308 --> 00:12:32,142
-So where'd he go?

237
00:12:32,175 --> 00:12:33,142
I don't see him anymore.

238
00:12:33,175 --> 00:12:35,008
-Do you suppose he's dead?

239
00:12:35,042 --> 00:12:36,508
